Topic Relevance
- use LSA (Bag of Words, TF-IDF) sklearn
- TF-IDF to TruncatedSVD
- cosine similarity between TruncatedSVD

Word Usage and Sentence complexity
- number of words, sentences, unique words, average word length

Grammar and Mechanics
- Language Tool (number of mistakes)

Features:
- Topic Relevance
    - Truncated TF-IDF Matrix
    - LSA Score(Similarity)

- Word Usage and Sentence complexity
    - Number of Words
    - Number of Sentences
    - Number of Unique Words
    - Average Word Length

- Grammar and Mechanics
    - Number of Mistakes(Spelling errors, Grammatical errors, etc.)
